 are a lifesaver. It consistently reminds me of tasks I completely forgot about. It's like having a personal assistant.\"\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"241\">\n            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--pink)] to-[var(--purple)] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\" data-kid=\"242\">PS</div>\n            <div data-kid=\"243\">\n              <div class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"244\">Priya Sharma</div>\n              <div class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text3)] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"245\">Product Manager, Pune</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[400px] bg-[var(--dark2)] p-8 rounded-3xl bento-border hover-lift cursor-default\" data-kid=\"246\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[var(--orange)] mb-6\" data-kid=\"247\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"248\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"249\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"250\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"251\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"252\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-[var(--text)] text-lg italic leading-relaxed mb-10\" data-kid=\"253\">\n            \"Best task app I've used. The interface is clean, dark mode is beautiful, and Focus Mode actually helps me get things done.\"\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"254\">\n            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--purple)] to-[var(--teal)] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\" data-kid=\"255\">KM</div>\n            <div data-kid=\"256\">\n              <div class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"257\">Karan Mehta</div>\n              <div class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text3)] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"258\">Software Engineer, Ahmedabad</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[400px] bg-[var(--dark2)] p-8 rounded-3xl bento-border hover-lift cursor-default\" data-kid=\"259\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[var(--orange)] mb-6\" data-kid=\"260\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"261\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"262\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"263\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"264\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"265\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-[var(--text)] text-lg italic leading-relaxed mb-10\" data-kid=\"266\">\n            \"Simple, effective, and free. I don't know why I was using complicated tools before. TaskMate is just better.\"\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"267\">\n            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--teal)] to-[var(--orange)] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\" data-kid=\"268\">SD</div>\n            <div data-kid=\"269\">\n              <div class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"270\">Siddharth Das</div>\n              <div class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text3)] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"271\">Content Creator, Mumbai</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <style data-kid=\"272\">\n      @keyframes scroll {\n        0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n        100% { transform: translateX(calc(-400px * 3 - 6px * 3)); }\n      }\n    </style>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section id=\"faq\" class=\"px-8 py-24 bg-[var(--dark)] relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"273\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[720px] mx-auto\" data-kid=\"274\">\n      <div class=\"text-center mb-16\" data-kid=\"275\">\n        <span class=\"text-[var(--teal)] text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] block mb-4\" data-kid=\"276\">FAQ</span>\n        <h2 class=\"text-[44px] font-bold tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"277\">Frequently asked questions</h2>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"space-y-6\" data-kid=\"278\">\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-[var(--dark2)] rounded-[32px] bento-border overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"279\">\n          <div class=\"px-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--border)] bg-white/5\" data-kid=\"280\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text3)]\" data-kid=\"281\">General</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"divide-y divide-[var(--border)]\" data-kid=\"282\">\n            <div class=\"p-8 bg-white/[0.02] border-l-4 border-[var(--purple)] group\" data-kid=\"283\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\" data-kid=\"284\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"285\">Is TaskMate AI really free?</h3>\n                <i class=\"ti ti-minus text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"286\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-[var(--text2)] text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"287\">Yes! The core features including unlimited tasks, voice input, and basic reminders are completely free forever. No credit card required.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-8 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors cursor-pointer group\" data-kid=\"288\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\" data-kid=\"289\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"290\">Which platforms is it available on?</h3>\n                <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-[var(--text3)] group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"291\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-[var(--text2)] text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"292\">TaskMate AI is currently available on Android via Google Play. An iOS version is coming soon, and you can also access your tasks through our Web App on any browser.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-[var(--dark2)] rounded-[32px] bento-border overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"293\">\n          <div class=\"px-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--border)] bg-white/5\" data-kid=\"294\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text3)]\" data-kid=\"295\">Technical</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"divide-y divide-[var(--border)]\" data-kid=\"296\">\n            <div class=\"p-8 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors cursor-pointer group\" data-kid=\"297\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\" data-kid=\"298\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"299\">How does the AI suggestion engine work?</h3>\n                <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-[var(--text3)] group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"300\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-[var(--text2)] text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"301\">Our AI uses advanced NLP to understand your natural language inputs and machine learning models to analyze your historical task completion patterns to suggest the most relevant actions.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-8 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors cursor-pointer group\" data-kid=\"302\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\" data-kid=\"303\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"304\">Can I use TaskMate offline?</h3>\n                <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-[var(--text3)] group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"305\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-[var(--text2)] text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"306\">Absolutely. TaskMate AI is built with an offline-first architecture. All your changes are saved locally and synced automatically as soon as you have an internet connection.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"px-8 py-24 bg-[var(--dark)]\" data-kid=\"307\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto bg-[var(--dark2)] rounded-[48px] bento-border p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"308\">\n      \n      <div class=\"absolute -top-[50%] -left-[20%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[var(--purple)]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"309\"></div>\n      <div class=\"absolute -bottom-[50%] -right-[20%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[var(--teal)]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"310\"></div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative z-10\" data-kid=\"311\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6\" data-kid=\"312\">Ready to plan smarter?</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-[var(--text2)] text-xl mb-12 max-w-[600px] mx-auto\" data-kid=\"313\">\n          Join 1,200+ users who transformed their productivity with TaskMate AI. Get started for free today.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"314\">\n          <button class=\"cta-pill px-10 py-5 rounded-full text-lg font-bold text-white cursor-pointer shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"315\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-brand-google-play text-2xl\" data-kid=\"316\"></i> Download Free on Android\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"px-10 py-5 rounded-full text-lg font-bold bento-border bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"317\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-brand-producthunt text-2xl\" data-kid=\"318\"></i> View on Product Hunt\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"px-8 pt-24 pb-12 bg-[var(--dark)] border-t border-[var(--border)]\" data-kid=\"319\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\" data-kid=\"320\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-20\" data-kid=\"321\">\n        \n        <div class=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-1\" data-kid=\"322\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\" data-kid=\"323\">\n            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bento-border\" data-kid=\"324\">\n              <img src=\"/api/local/images/assets/logo.png\" alt=\"TaskMate Logo\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"325\">\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"326\">TaskMate <span class=\"text-[var(--purple)]\" data-kid=\"327\">AI</span></span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm mb-6 max-w-[200px]\" data-kid=\"328\">\n            The most intelligent way to manage your tasks and life.\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text3)] font-medium flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"329\">\n            Made in Ahmedabad 🇮🇳\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div data-kid=\"330\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8\" data-kid=\"331\">Product</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"332\">\n            <li data-kid=\"333\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"334\">Features</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"335\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"336\">How it works</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"337\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"338\">Pricing</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"339\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"340\">Release Notes</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div data-kid=\"341\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8\" data-kid=\"342\">Company</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"343\">\n            <li data-kid=\"344\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"345\">About Us</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"346\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"347\">Careers</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"348\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"349\">Contact</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"350\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"351\">Blog</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div data-kid=\"352\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8\" data-kid=\"353\">Legal</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"354\">\n            <li data-kid=\"355\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"356\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"357\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"358\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"359\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-sm hover:text-[var(--teal)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"360\">Cookie Policy</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"pt-12 border-t border-[var(--border)] flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 opacity-60\" data-kid=\"361\">\n        <p class=\"text-[var(--text3)] text-xs\" data-kid=\"362\">© 2024 TaskMate AI. All rights reserved. Ahmedabad, India.</p>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"363\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"364\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-twitter text-xl\" data-kid=\"365\"></i></a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"366\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-github text-xl\" data-kid=\"367\"></i></a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--text3)] hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"368\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-linkedin text-xl\" data-kid=\"369\"></i></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>\n",
