 </div>\n                        <p class=\"text-lg italic mb-8 opacity-90 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"307\">\"Clean UI, smart features, and the focus mode is exactly what I needed to finish my thesis.\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"308\">\n                            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"309\">MP</div>\n                            <div data-kid=\"310\">\n                                <h4 class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"311\">Meera Patel</h4>\n                                <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"312\">PhD Student</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"w-[380px] shrink-0 p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--purple)]/30 transition-all\" data-kid=\"313\">\n                        <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-6\" data-kid=\"314\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"315\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"316\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"317\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"318\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"319\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"text-lg italic mb-8 opacity-90 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"320\">\"Best productivity app I've used in years. The Android widgets are actually useful and look great.\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"321\">\n                            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"322\">SJ</div>\n                            <div data-kid=\"323\">\n                                <h4 class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"324\">Siddharth Jain</h4>\n                                <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"325\">Software Engineer</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"w-[380px] shrink-0 p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--purple)]/30 transition-all\" data-kid=\"326\">\n                        <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-6\" data-kid=\"327\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"328\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"329\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"330\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"331\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"332\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"text-lg italic mb-8 opacity-90 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"333\">\"Collaboration features for my team are top-notch. Everyone stays in the loop effortlessly.\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"334\">\n                            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-teal-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"335\">KD</div>\n                            <div data-kid=\"336\">\n                                <h4 class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"337\">Kritika Das</h4>\n                                <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"338\">Marketing Lead</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"flex gap-6\" data-kid=\"339\">\n                    <div class=\"w-[380px] shrink-0 p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--purple)]/30 transition-all\" data-kid=\"340\">\n                        <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-6\" data-kid=\"341\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"342\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"343\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"344\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"345\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"346\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"text-lg italic mb-8 opacity-90 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"347\">\"TaskMate AI actually feels like it knows my brain. The voice capture is a lifesaver when I'm driving.\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"348\">\n                            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"349\">AS</div>\n                            <div data-kid=\"350\">\n                                <h4 class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"351\">Ananya Sharma</h4>\n                                <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"352\">Product Designer</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"w-[380px] shrink-0 p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--purple)]/30 transition-all\" data-kid=\"353\">\n                        <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-6\" data-kid=\"354\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"355\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"356\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"357\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"358\"></i><i class=\"ti ti-star-filled\" data-kid=\"359\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"text-lg italic mb-8 opacity-90 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"360\">\"The AI schedule optimization has saved me at least 4 hours of planning every single week. Incredible.\"</p>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"361\">\n                            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-teal-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"362\">RV</div>\n                            <div data-kid=\"363\">\n                                <h4 class=\"font-bold\" data-kid=\"364\">Rahul Verma</h4>\n                                <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"365\">Startup Founder</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section id=\"faq\" class=\"py-32 bg-[var(--bg-primary)]\" data-kid=\"366\">\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"367\">\n            <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"368\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16 reveal\" data-kid=\"369\">Frequently asked questions</h2>\n                <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"370\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"reveal faq-item bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-3xl p-6 transition-all\" data-kid=\"371\">\n                        <button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" data-kid=\"372\">\n                            <span class=\"text-lg font-bold\" data-kid=\"373\">Is TaskMate AI really free?</span>\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-xl transition-transform duration-300\" data-kid=\"374\"></i>\n                        </button>\n                        <div class=\"faq-content max-h-0 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"375\">\n                            <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"376\">Yes! Our Free tier includes all core AI features, limited to 50 tasks per day. It's perfect for individuals wanting to test the power of AI productivity without any cost.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"reveal faq-item bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-3xl p-6 transition-all\" data-kid=\"377\">\n                        <button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" data-kid=\"378\">\n                            <span class=\"text-lg font-bold\" data-kid=\"379\">Which platforms is it available on?</span>\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-xl transition-transform duration-300\" data-kid=\"380\"></i>\n                        </button>\n                        <div class=\"faq-content max-h-0 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"381\">\n                            <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"382\">TaskMate AI is currently live on Android and available via our Web App. Our iOS app is currently in beta and launching very soon on the App Store.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"reveal faq-item bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-3xl p-6 transition-all\" data-kid=\"383\">\n                        <button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" data-kid=\"384\">\n                            <span class=\"text-lg font-bold\" data-kid=\"385\">How does the AI suggestion engine work?</span>\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-xl transition-transform duration-300\" data-kid=\"386\"></i>\n                        </button>\n                        <div class=\"faq-content max-h-0 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"387\">\n                            <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"388\">Our engine uses a proprietary model that analyzes your task deadlines, predicted effort, and historical peak productivity hours to suggest a personalized daily agenda.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"reveal faq-item bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-3xl p-6 transition-all\" data-kid=\"389\">\n                        <button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" data-kid=\"390\">\n                            <span class=\"text-lg font-bold\" data-kid=\"391\">Can I use TaskMate offline?</span>\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-xl transition-transform duration-300\" data-kid=\"392\"></i>\n                        </button>\n                        <div class=\"faq-content max-h-0 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"393\">\n                            <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"394\">Absolutely. TaskMate allows you to add and edit tasks offline. Your changes will automatically sync once you're back online.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"reveal faq-item bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-3xl p-6 transition-all\" data-kid=\"395\">\n                        <button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\" data-kid=\"396\">\n                            <span class=\"text-lg font-bold\" data-kid=\"397\">Is team collaboration available?</span>\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-xl transition-transform duration-300\" data-kid=\"398\"></i>\n                        </button>\n                        <div class=\"faq-content max-h-0 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"399\">\n                            <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"400\">Yes, our Team tier is designed for collaborative workspaces. It includes shared project boards, team-wide priorities, and advanced admin controls.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section class=\"reveal py-32 relative\" data-kid=\"401\">\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"402\">\n            <div class=\"relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--purple)]/20 via-[var(--bg-secondary)] to-[var(--teal)]/20 rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-24 text-center overflow-hidden border border-[var(--border)]\" data-kid=\"403\">\n                <div class=\"relative z-10\" data-kid=\"404\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-8\" data-kid=\"405\">Ready to plan smarter?</h2>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12\" data-kid=\"406\">Join 1,200+ users who have transformed their life with TaskMate AI. Download for free today.</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"407\">\n                        <button class=\"w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-[var(--grad-cta)] text-white font-black rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"408\">Download for Android</button>\n                        <button class=\"w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 border border-white/10 bg-white/5 font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"409\">See on Product Hunt</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png')] opacity-5\" data-kid=\"410\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <footer class=\"py-20 bg-[var(--bg-primary)] border-t border-[var(--border)]\" data-kid=\"411\">\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"412\">\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-20\" data-kid=\"413\">\n                <div class=\"lg:col-span-1\" data-kid=\"414\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\" data-kid=\"415\">\n                        <svg class=\"w-8 h-8\" viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-kid=\"416\">\n                            <rect width=\"40\" height=\"40\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"url(#logoGradFooter)\" data-kid=\"417\"></rect>\n                            <defs data-kid=\"418\">\n                                <linearGradient id=\"logoGradFooter\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"40\" y2=\"0\" data-kid=\"419\">\n                                    <stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#F5A87B\" data-kid=\"420\"></stop>\n                                    <stop offset=\"30%\" stop-color=\"#F0607A\" data-kid=\"421\"></stop>\n                                    <stop offset=\"65%\" stop-color=\"#8B65C8\" data-kid=\"422\"></stop>\n                                    <stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#4ABFB8\" data-kid=\"423\"></stop>\n                                </linearGradient>\n                            </defs>\n                            <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"20\" r=\"11\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" data-kid=\"424\"></circle>\n                            <path d=\"M14 20.5L18 24.5L26 16\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"425\"></path>\n                        </svg>\n                        <span class=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"426\">TaskMate AI</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"427\">Reimagining productivity for the AI era. Plan smarter, live better.</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"428\">Made with ❤️ in Ahmedabad, India 🇮🇳</p>\n                </div>\n                <div data-kid=\"429\">\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-6\" data-kid=\"430\">Product</h4>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]\" data-kid=\"431\">\n                        <li data-kid=\"432\"><a href=\"#features\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"433\">Features</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"434\"><a href=\"#how-it-works\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"435\">How it works</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"436\"><a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"437\">Pricing</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"438\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"439\">Release Notes</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div data-kid=\"440\">\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-6\" data-kid=\"441\">Company</h4>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]\" data-kid=\"442\">\n                        <li data-kid=\"443\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"444\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"445\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"446\">Careers</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"447\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"448\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"449\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--purple)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"450\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div data-kid=\"451\">\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-6\" data-kid=\"452\">Social</h4>\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"453\">\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-[var(--purple)] hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"454\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-x\" data-kid=\"455\"></i></a>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-[var(--purple)] hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"456\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-linkedin\" data-kid=\"457\"></i></a>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-[var(--purple)] hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"458\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-github\" data-kid=\"459\"></i></a>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-[var(--purple)] hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"460\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram\" data-kid=\"461\"></i></a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pt-10 border-t border-[var(--border)] flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"462\">\n                <p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"463\">© 2025 TaskMate AI. All rights reserved.</p>\n                <div class=\"flex gap-8 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\" data-kid=\"464\">\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"465\">Security</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"466\">Status</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"467\">Cookies</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</div>\n\n<script data-kid=\"468\">\n    // Theme Toggle Logic\n    const html = document.documentElement;\n    const themeToggle = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');\n    const themeIcon = document.getElementById('theme-icon');\n\n    const updateIcon = (isDark) => {\n        themeIcon.className = isDark ? 'ti ti-moon-stars' : 'ti ti-sun';\n    };\n\n    const toggleTheme = () => {\n        const isDark = html.dataset.theme === 'dark';\n        const newTheme = isDark ? 'light' : 'dark';\n        html.dataset.theme = newTheme;\n        localStorage.setItem('theme', newTheme);\n        updateIcon(!isDark);\n    };\n\n    // Initialize Theme\n    const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'dark';\n    html.dataset.theme = savedTheme;\n    updateIcon(savedTheme === 'dark');\n    themeToggle.addEventListener('click', toggleTheme);\n\n\n    // Mobile Menu\n    const mobileToggle = document.getElementById('mobile-toggle');\n    const mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');\n    mobileToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        mobileMenu.classList.toggle('open');\n        const icon = mobileToggle.querySelector('i');\n        icon.className = mobileMenu.classList.contains('open') ? 'ti ti-x' : 'ti ti-menu-2';\n    });\n    // Close mobile menu on link click\n    mobileMenu.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(link => {\n        link.addEventListener('click', () => {\n            mobileMenu.classList.remove('open');\n            mobileToggle.querySelector('i').className = 'ti ti-menu-2';\n        });\n    });\n\n    // Immediate activation for content and stats in iframe\n    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n        document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => el.classList.add('visible'));\n        setTimeout(startStatsCounter, 800);\n    });\n\n    // Stats Count Up\n    function countUp(el, target, duration = 2000) {\n        let start = 0;\n        const decimals = parseInt(el.dataset.decimal) || 0;\n        const startTime = performance.now();\n\n        function update(currentTime) {\n            const elapsedTime = currentTime - startTime;\n            const progress = Math.min(elapsedTime / duration, 1);\n            \n            // Ease out cubic\n            const ease = 1 - Math.pow(1 - progress, 3);\n            const currentValue = (ease * target).toFixed(decimals);\n            \n            el.textContent = currentValue;\n\n            if (progress < 1) {\n                requestAnimationFrame(update);\n            } else {\n                el.textContent = target;\n            }\n        }\n        requestAnimationFrame(update);\n    }\n\n    let statsStarted = false;\n    function startStatsCounter() {\n        if (statsStarted) return;\n        statsStarted = true;\n        document.querySelectorAll('.stat-number').forEach(el => {\n            const target = parseFloat(el.dataset.target);\n            countUp(el, target);\n        });\n    }\n\n    // How It Works Step Switcher\n    function switchStep(index) {\n        document.querySelectorAll('.step-btn').forEach((btn, i) => {\n            btn.classList.toggle('active', i === index);\n        });\n        \n        const panels = document.querySelectorAll('.panel-content');\n        panels.forEach((panel, i) => {\n            if (i === index) {\n                panel.style.display = 'block';\n                // Trigger reflow for transition\n                panel.offsetHeight;\n                panel.classList.remove('hidden');\n            } else {\n                panel.classList.add('hidden');\n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    if (panel.classList.contains('hidden')) {\n                        panel.style.display = 'none';\n                    }\n                }, 400);\n            }\n        });\n    }\n\n    // FAQ Accordion\n    function toggleFaq(btn) {\n        const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');\n        const isActive = item.classList.contains('active');\n        \n        // Close others\n        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(el => {\n            el.classList.remove('active');\n        });\n\n        if (!isActive) {\n            item.classList.add('active');\n        }\n    }\n\n    // Pricing Toggle\n    const toggleMonthly = document.getElementById('toggle-monthly');\n    const toggleAnnual = document.getElementById('toggle-annual');\n    const priceElements = document.querySelectorAll('.price-value');\n\n    toggleMonthly.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        toggleMonthly.classList.add('bg-[var(--purple)]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg');\n        toggleMonthly.classList.remove('text-[var(--text-secondary)]');\n        toggleAnnual.classList.remove('bg-[var(--purple)]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg');\n        toggleAnnual.classList.add('text-[var(--text-secondary)]');\n        \n        priceElements.forEach(el => {\n            const val = el.dataset.monthly;\n            el.innerHTML = `₹${val}<span class=\"text-lg text-[var(--text-muted)] font-bold\">/mo</span>`;\n        });\n    });\n\n    toggleAnnual.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        toggleAnnual.classList.add('bg-[var(--purple)]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg');\n        toggleAnnual.classList.remove('text-[var(--text-secondary)]');\n        toggleMonthly.classList.remove('bg-[var(--purple)]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg');\n        toggleMonthly.classList.add('text-[var(--text-secondary)]');\n        \n        priceElements.forEach(el => {\n            const val = el.dataset.annual;\n            el.innerHTML = `₹${val}<span class=\"text-lg text-[var(--text-muted)] font-bold\">/mo</span>`;\n        });\n    });\n\n\n</script>\n",
