5xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)]\" data-kid=\"106\">The Power of Intelligence</h2>\n                <p class=\"text-[var(--text-secondary)] max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg\" data-kid=\"107\">We've built the most comprehensive productivity toolset ever put into an app.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\" data-kid=\"108\">\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal group bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[var(--purple)]/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(139,101,200,0.15)] transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"109\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--purple)]/10 text-[var(--purple)] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"110\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-microphone-2 text-3xl\" data-kid=\"111\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"112\">Voice to Task</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"113\">Just tap and talk. Our AI extracts dates, times, and priority levels directly from your natural speech.</p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal group bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[var(--pink)]/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(240,96,122,0.15)] transition-all duration-500\" style=\"transition-delay: 0.1s;\" data-kid=\"114\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--pink)]/10 text-[var(--pink)] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"115\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-sparkles text-3xl\" data-kid=\"116\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"117\">Smart Suggestions</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"118\">TaskMate learns your productive peaks and suggests when to tackle your hardest tasks for maximum output.</p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal group bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[var(--teal)]/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(74,191,184,0.15)] transition-all duration-500\" style=\"transition-delay: 0.2s;\" data-kid=\"119\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--teal)]/10 text-[var(--teal)] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"120\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-bell-ringing text-3xl\" data-kid=\"121\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"122\">Smart Reminders</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"123\">Location-based alerts that ping you exactly when you're at the office or the grocery store. Never forget again.</p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal group bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[var(--orange)]/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(245,168,123,0.15)] transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"124\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--orange)]/10 text-[var(--orange)] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"125\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-calendar-event text-3xl\" data-kid=\"126\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"127\">Calendar Sync</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"128\">Automatically pulls meetings from your calendars and blocks out time for your tasks around them.</p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal group bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[var(--purple)]/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(139,101,200,0.15)] transition-all duration-500\" style=\"transition-delay: 0.1s;\" data-kid=\"129\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--purple)]/10 text-[var(--purple)] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"130\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-target-arrow text-3xl\" data-kid=\"131\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"132\">Focus Mode Pro</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"133\">Enter a flow state with integrated Pomodoro timers and AI-generated ambient soundscapes that boost concentration.</p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal group bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border)] p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[var(--teal)]/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(74,191,184,0.15)] transition-all duration-500\" style=\"transition-delay: 0.2s;\" data-kid=\"134\">\n                    <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[var(--teal)]/10 text-[var(--teal)] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"135\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-layout-2 text-3xl\" data-kid=\"136\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4\" data-kid=\"137\">Home Widgets</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"138\">Stunning Material You widgets that look beautiful on your home screen and keep your agenda visible.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section id=\"how-it-works\" class=\"py-32 bg-[var(--bg-tertiary)]/30 border-y border-[var(--border)] overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"139\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4\" data-kid=\"140\">\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\" data-kid=\"141\">\n                \n                <div class=\"reveal space-y-12\" data-kid=\"142\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)]\" data-kid=\"143\">Built for Speed.</h2>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-6 relative\" data-kid=\"144\">\n                        \n                        <div class=\"absolute left-7 top-10 bottom-10 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--purple)] via-[var(--pink)] to-transparent\" data-kid=\"145\"></div>\n                        \n                        \n                        <div class=\"step-card active cursor-pointer p-8 rounded-3xl border border-[var(--purple)]/50 bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] shadow-xl relative z-10 transition-all duration-300 group\" onclick=\"switchStep(0)\" data-kid=\"146\">\n                            <div class=\"flex gap-8\" data-kid=\"147\">\n                                <div class=\"shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[var(--purple)] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(139,101,200,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"148\">1</div>\n                                <div class=\"space-y-2\" data-kid=\"149\">\n                                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)]\" data-kid=\"150\">Add tasks by voice or type</h4>\n                                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] group-[.active]:text-[var(--text-secondary)]\" data-kid=\"151\">Just speak naturally. No complicated forms or menus needed.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"step-card cursor-pointer p-8 rounded-3xl border border-transparent hover:bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]/50 relative z-10 transition-all duration-300 group\" onclick=\"switchStep(1)\" data-kid=\"152\">\n                            <div class=\"flex gap-8\" data-kid=\"153\">\n                                <div class=\"shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-tertiary)] border border-[var(--border)] text-[var(--text-muted)] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl group-[.active]:bg-[var(--pink)] group-[.active]:text-white group-[.active]:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(240,96,122,0.4)] group-[.active]:border-transparent transition-all\" data-kid=\"154\">2</div>\n                                <div class=\"space-y-2\" data-kid=\"155\">\n                                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)]\" data-kid=\"156\">AI organizes your day</h4>\n                                    <p class=\"text-[var(--text-muted)] group-[.active]:text-[var(--text-secondary)]\" data-kid=\"157\">The engine optimizes your schedule based on context and priority.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n                        <div class=\"step-card cursor-pointer p-8 rounded-3xl border border-transparent hover:bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]/50 relative z-10 transition-all duration-300 group\" onclick=\"switchStep(2)\" data-kid=\"158\">\n                            <div class=\"flex gap-8\" data-kid=\"159\">\n                                <div class=\"shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-tertiary)] border border-[var(--border)] text-[va