nter justify-center mb-12\" data-kid=\"193\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-bolt text-[#6C3AED] text-2xl\" data-kid=\"194\"></i>\n                        </span>\n                        <h4 class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"195\">AI Priority Engine</h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-white/50 text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-lg\" data-kid=\"196\">TaskMate identifies your \"one thing\" every single day, aggressively silencing notifications until it's delivered.</p>\n                        \n                        <div class=\"mt-16 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-md\" data-kid=\"197\">\n                            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\" data-kid=\"198\">\n                                <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40\" data-kid=\"199\">Daily Focus</span>\n                                <span class=\"text-[#6C3AED] text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"200\">85% Complete</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"w-full h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"201\">\n                                <div class=\"w-4/5 h-full bg-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"202\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"md:col-span-5 space-y-12\" data-kid=\"203\">\n                    <div class=\"p-4 border-b border-[#E8E8E8]\" data-kid=\"204\">\n                        <h5 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"205\"><i class=\"ti ti-layout-kanban text-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"206\"></i> Smart Boards</h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#555] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"207\">Dynamic boards that rearrange themselves based on your daily energy patterns.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-4 border-b border-[#E8E8E8]\" data-kid=\"208\">\n                        <h5 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"209\"><i class=\"ti ti-users text-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"210\"></i> Team Sync</h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#555] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"211\">Real-time collaboration with AI mediation to remove meeting fatigue.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-4 border-b border-[#E8E8E8]\" data-kid=\"212\">\n                        <h5 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"213\"><i class=\"ti ti-cloud-off text-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"214\"></i> Offline First</h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#555] leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"215\">Work anywhere. Sync happens instantly the moment you're back online.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"216\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16 text-center\" data-kid=\"217\">\n             <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#0A0A0A]\" data-kid=\"218\">Built for high-performers.</h2>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8\" data-kid=\"219\">\n            <div id=\"marquee-1\" class=\"flex gap-8 items-center py-4 whitespace-nowrap\" data-kid=\"220\">\n                \n            </div>\n            <div id=\"marquee-2\" class=\"flex gap-8 items-center py-4 whitespace-nowrap\" data-kid=\"221\">\n                \n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section id=\"pricing\" class=\"py-32 bg-[#F7F7F7]\" data-kid=\"222\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"223\">\n            <div class=\"mb-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end gap-12\" data-kid=\"224\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black text-[#0A0A0A] tracking-tighter leading-[0.85]\" data-kid=\"225\">Invest in <br data-kid=\"226\"> your focus.</h2>\n                <p class=\"text-[#999] max-w-xs font-mono text-sm uppercase\" data-kid=\"227\">Transparent tiers for every stage of growth.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\" data-kid=\"228\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse\" data-kid=\"229\">\n                    <thead data-kid=\"230\">\n                        <tr class=\"text-left border-b-4 border-[#0A0A0A]\" data-kid=\"231\">\n                            <th class=\"py-8 text-2xl font-black\" data-kid=\"232\">Feature</th>\n                            <th class=\"py-8 px-6 text-2xl font-black\" data-kid=\"233\">Personal</th>\n                            <th class=\"py-8 px-6 text-2xl font-black text-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"234\">Pro Tier</th>\n                            <th class=\"py-8 px-6 text-2xl font-black\" data-kid=\"235\">Enterprise</th>\n                        </tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-[#E8E8E8] font-medium\" data-kid=\"236\">\n                        <tr data-kid=\"237\">\n                            <td class=\"py-6 font-bold\" data-kid=\"238\">Autonomous Priority</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6\" data-kid=\"239\">Basic</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6 text-[#6C3AED] font-bold\" data-kid=\"240\">Neural Engine</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6\" data-kid=\"241\">Custom Models</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr data-kid=\"242\">\n                            <td class=\"py-6 font-bold\" data-kid=\"243\">Calendar Auto-Sync</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6\" data-kid=\"244\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" data-kid=\"245\"></i></td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6 text-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"246\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" data-kid=\"247\"></i></td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6\" data-kid=\"248\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" data-kid=\"249\"></i></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr data-kid=\"250\">\n                            <td class=\"py-6 font-bold\" data-kid=\"251\">Cognitive Load Analysis</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6 text-white/0\" data-kid=\"252\">—</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6 text-[#6C3AED] font-bold\" data-kid=\"253\">Real-time</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6\" data-kid=\"254\">Organization-wide</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr data-kid=\"255\">\n                            <td class=\"py-6 font-bold\" data-kid=\"256\">Deep Work Analytics</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6 text-white/0\" data-kid=\"257\">—</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6 text-[#6C3AED] font-bold\" data-kid=\"258\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" data-kid=\"259\"></i></td>\n                            <td class=\"py-6 px-6\" data-kid=\"260\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" data-kid=\"261\"></i></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"bg-[#0A0A0A]/5\" data-kid=\"262\">\n                            <td class=\"py-12 text-xl font-black\" data-kid=\"263\">Monthly Investment</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-12 px-6 text-3xl font-black\" data-kid=\"264\">$0</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-12 px-6 text-5xl font-black text-[#6C3AED]\" data-kid=\"265\">$19</td>\n                            <td class=\"py-12 px-6 text-3xl font-black\" data-kid=\"266\">Custom</td>\n                        </tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section id=\"final-cta\" class=\"relative w-full h-[80vh] bg-[#0A0A0A] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"267\">\n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(108,58,237,0.2),transparent_70%)] opacity-50 z-0\" data-kid=\"268\"></div>\n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10\" id=\"cta-particles\" data-kid=\"269\"></div>\n        \n        <div class=\"relative z-10 px-6 max-w-4xl\" data-kid=\"270\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"271\">Ready to let AI run <br data-kid=\"272\"> your workflow?</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-white/40 text-lg md:text-xl font-['IBM_Plex_Mono'] mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"273\">Join 50,000+ high-performers reclaiming their focus today.</p>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center\" data-kid=\"274\">\n                <button class=\"px-10 py-5 bg-[#6C3AED] text-white rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-[#5A2DD1] transition-transform hover:scale-110 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(108,58,237,0.3)]\" data-kid=\"275\">Get Early Access</button>\n                <button class=\"px-10 py-5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors backdrop-blur-xl\" data-kid=\"276\">Download for Mobile</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <footer class=\"bg-white py-24 border-t border-[#E8E8E8]\" data-kid=\"277\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"278\">\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 mb-20\" data-kid=\"279\">\n                <div class=\"col-span-2\" data-kid=\"280\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\" data-kid=\"281\">\n                        <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-[#6C3AED] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"282\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-atom text-white\" data-kid=\"283\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <span class=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0A0A0A]\" data-kid=\"284\">TaskMate AI</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-[#555] text-sm max-w-xs leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"285\">The intelligent orchestration layer for modern professionals. Automate the administrative, focus on the creative.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div data-kid=\"286\">\n                    <h5 class=\"font-bold text-[#0A0A0A] mb-6\" data-kid=\"287\">Product</h5>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-[#555]\" data-kid=\"288\">\n                        <li data-kid=\"289\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"290\">Features</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"291\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"292\">Security</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"293\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"294\">Enterprise</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"295\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"296\">Integrations</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div data-kid=\"297\">\n                    <h5 class=\"font-bold text-[#0A0A0A] mb-6\" data-kid=\"298\">Company</h5>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-[#555]\" data-kid=\"299\">\n                        <li data-kid=\"300\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"301\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"302\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"303\">Careers</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"304\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"305\">Newsroom</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"306\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"307\">Contact</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div data-kid=\"308\">\n                    <h5 class=\"font-bold text-[#0A0A0A] mb-6\" data-kid=\"309\">Resources</h5>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-[#555]\" data-kid=\"310\">\n                        <li data-kid=\"311\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"312\">Documentation</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"313\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"314\">Help Center</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"315\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"316\">Privacy</a></li>\n                        <li data-kid=\"317\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#6C3AED] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"318\">Terms</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-[#E8E8E8] flex flex-col md:row justify-between items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"319\">\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-[#999]\" data-kid=\"320\">© 2026 TaskMate AI. All rights reserved.</p>\n                <div class=\"flex gap-6\" data-kid=\"321\">\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[#999] hover:text-[#0A0A0A] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"322\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-twitter\" data-kid=\"323\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[#999] hover:text-[#0A0A0A] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"324\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-github\" data-kid=\"325\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[#999] hover:text-[#0A0A0A] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"326\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-linkedin\" data-kid=\"327\"></i></a>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-xs text-[#999]\" data-kid=\"328\">Made with ❤️ by CK Future Tech</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</div>\n\n<style data-kid=\"329\">\n    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');\n    @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css');\n    @import url('https://unpkg.com/lenis@1/dist/lenis.css');\n\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n        background: #0A0A0A;\n    }\n\n    /* Custom Perspective */\n    .perspective-1000 {\n        perspective: 1000px;\n    }\n\n    /* Scrollbar */\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar {\n        width: 8px;\n    }\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n        background: #0A0A0A;\n    }\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n        background: #333;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n        background: #6C3AED;\n    }\n\n    .chaos-card {\n        will-change: transform, opacity;\n    }\n\n    .kanban-card {\n        will-change: transform, box-shadow;\n    }\n\n    /* Marquee Animation Classes (GSAP handles better, but CSS fallback) */\n    @keyframes marquee {\n        0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n        100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n    }\n    @keyframes marquee-reverse {\n        0% { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n        100% { transform: translateX(0); }\n    }\n</style>\n\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"330\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"331\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/TextPlugin.min.js\" data-kid=\"332\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/split-type\" data-kid=\"333\"></script>\n<script type=\"module\" data-kid=\"334\">\n    import Lenis from \"https://esm.sh/lenis@1\"\n    \n    // Initialize Plugins\n    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger, TextPlugin);\n    \n    // Initialize Lenis\n    const lenis = new Lenis();\n    lenis.on('scroll', ScrollTrigger.update);\n    gsap.ticker.add((time) => {\n        lenis.raf(time * 1000);\n    });\n    gsap.ticker.lagSmoothing(0);\n\n    // Helper: Random between\n    const random = (min, max) => Math.random() * (max - min) + min;\n\n    // --- Hero Animations ---\n    const heroSplit = new SplitType('#hero-headline', { types: 'chars' });\n    \n    const heroTl = gsap.timeline();\n    heroTl.from(heroSplit.chars, {\n        y: 100,\n        opacity: 0,\n        stagger: 0.02,\n        duration: 1.5,\n        ease: 'expo.out'\n    })\n    .to('#hero-subheadline', { opacity: 1, duration: 1 }, \"-=1\")\n    .to('#hero-actions', { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 1 }, \"-=0.5\")\n    .to('#hero-stats', { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 1 }, \"-=0.5\");\n\n    // Magnetic Core Effect\n    const core = document.querySelector('.hero-core-wrapper');\n    window.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {\n        const { clientX, clientY } = e;\n        const x = (clientX - window.innerWidth / 2) * 0.05;\n        const y = (clientY - window.innerHeight / 2) * 0.05;\n        gsap.to(core, { x, y, duration: 0.8, ease: 'power2.out' });\n    });\n\n    // --- Chaos Section Generation & Animation ---\n    const chaosContainer = document.querySelector('#scatter-tasks');\n    const taskPhrases = [\n        \"Finalize Q3 QBR presentation\", \"Respond to urgent legal query\", \"Pay cloud bills\",\n        \"Update roadmap\", \"Client call #402\", \"Bug #912 priority\", \"Interview candidate X\",\n        \"Team standup missing notes\", \"Approve PR #122\", \"Security patch\", \"Database migration\",\n        \"Office lease renewal\", \"Marketing brief\", \"Review KPIs\", \"Tax filing\", \"Sprint planning\",\n        \"Check inbox (492+)\", \"Slack DM from boss\", \"Server offline alert\", \"Unfinished project A\",\n        \"Feedback loop\", \"Onboarding docs\", \"Expense reports\", \"Product demo prep\",\n        \"Security audit\", \"Legacy code refactor\", \"Investor update\", \"API rate limit reached\"\n    ];\n\n    taskPhrases.forEach((text, i) => {\n        const card = document.createElement('div');\n        card.className = `chaos-card absolute p-4 bg-white text-[#0A0A0A] rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-56 pointer-events-none border-l-4 ${i % 3 === 0 ? 'border-red-500' : 'border-[#E8E8E8]'}`;\n        card.innerHTML = `\n            <div class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-red-500 font-bold mb-1 uppercase tracking-widest\">${i % 3 === 0 ? 'Urgent' : 'Overdue'}</div>\n            <p class=\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight\">${text}</p>\n        `;\n        \n        // Random placement\n        gsap.set(card, {\n            left: `${random(5, 85)}%`,\n            top: `${random(5, 85)}%`,\n            rotation: random(-25, 25),\n            scale: random(0.8, 1.2),\n            opacity: random(0.3, 0.8)\n        });\n        \n        chaosContainer.appendChild(card);\n    });\n\n    // Chaos Scroll Trigger\n    gsap.to('.chaos-card', {\n        x: (i) => (i % 2 === 0 ? 100 : -100),\n        y: (i) => (i % 3 === 0 ? 100 : -100),\n        rotation: (i) => (i % 2 === 0 ? 360 : -360),\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#chaos',\n            start: 'top top',\n            end: 'bottom bottom',\n            scrub: 1\n        }\n    });\n\n    gsap.to('#chaos-headline', {\n        scale: 1.2,\n        opacity: 0,\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#chaos',\n            start: '50% top',\n            end: 'bottom bottom',\n            scrub: true\n        }\n    });\n\n    // --- AI Understands Animation ---\n    const understandLines = document.querySelector('#understand-lines');\n    \n    // Draw lines from scattered positions to center\n    for(let i=0; i<15; i++) {\n        const line = document.createElementNS(\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\", \"line\");\n        const x1 = random(0, 100);\n        const y1 = random(0, 100);\n        line.setAttribute(\"x1\", `${x1}%`);\n        line.setAttribute(\"y1\", `${y1}%`);\n        line.setAttribute(\"x2\", \"50%\");\n        line.setAttribute(\"y2\", \"50%\");\n        line.setAttribute(\"stroke\", \"#6C3AED\");\n        line.setAttribute(\"stroke-width\", \"1\");\n        line.setAttribute(\"stroke-dasharray\", \"10,10\");\n        line.classList.add(\"understand-path\");\n        understandLines.appendChild(line);\n    }\n\n    gsap.from('.understand-path', {\n        attr: { x1: \"50%\", y1: \"50%\" },\n        opacity: 0,\n        stagger: 0.05,\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#understand',\n            start: 'top top',\n            end: '50% center',\n            scrub: 1\n        }\n    });\n\n    gsap.to('#understand-core', {\n        scale: 4,\n        opacity: 0.6,\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#understand',\n            start: 'top top',\n            end: '50% top',\n            scrub: true\n        }\n    });\n\n    gsap.to('#understand-core-visual', {\n        opacity: 1,\n        scale: 1,\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#understand',\n            start: '30% top',\n            end: '60% top',\n            scrub: true\n        }\n    });\n\n    // --- AI Organizes (Masonry to Kanban) ---\n    const sortingContainer = document.querySelector('#sorting-container');\n    const kanbanTasks = [\n        { title: \"Fix server latency\", priority: \"High\", col: 0 },\n        { title: \"Approve landing page\", priority: \"High\", col: 0 },\n        { title: \"Weekly engineering sync\", priority: \"Med\", col: 1 },\n        { title: \"Send client invoices\", priority: \"Low\", col: 2 },\n        { title: \"Prepare demo deck\", priority: \"Med\", col: 1 },\n        { title: \"Legal review\", priority: \"High\", col: 0 },\n        { title: \"Update tax info\", priority: \"Low\", col: 2 },\n        { title: \"Cloud migration\", priority: \"High\", col: 0 },\n        { title: \"Hire PM role\", priority: \"Med\", col: 1 }\n    ];\n\n    kanbanTasks.forEach((task, i) => {\n        const card = document.createElement('div');\n        card.className = `sorting-card absolute p-6 bg-white border border-[#E8E8E8] rounded-[1.5rem] w-72 shadow-xl`;\n        card.innerHTML = `\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">\n                <div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full ${task.priority === 'High' ? 'bg-red-500' : task.priority === 'Med' ? 'bg-blue-500' : 'bg-emerald-500'}\"></div>\n                <span class=\"text-[9px] font-bold uppercase text-[#999] tracking-widest\">${task.priority} Priority</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"font-bold text-base text-[#0A0A0A] leading-tight\">${task.title}</p>\n        `;\n        \n        // Initial \"Chaos\" state for masonry\n        gsap.set(card, {\n            left: `${random(10, 80)}%`,\n            top: `${random(10, 70)}%`,\n            rotation: random(-30, 30),\n            opacity: 0,\n            scale: 0.5\n        });\n        \n        sortingContainer.appendChild(card);\n    });\n\n    const sortingTl = gsap.timeline({\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#organize',\n            start: 'top top',\n            end: 'bottom bottom',\n            scrub: 1,\n            pin: true\n        }\n    });\n\n    sortingTl.to('.sorting-card', {\n        opacity: 1,\n        scale: 1,\n        stagger: 0.05,\n        duration: 0.8\n    })\n    .to('#organize-headline', {\n        text: \"Organizing...\",\n        duration: 0.8\n    })\n    .to('.sorting-card', {\n        left: (i) => `${15 + kanbanTasks[i].col * 28}%`,\n        top: (i) => `${25 + (Math.floor(i / 3)) * 25}%`,\n        rotation: 0,\n        duration: 1.5,\n        ease: 'expo.inOut'\n    })\n    .to('#organize-headline', {\n        text: \"Prioritizing...\",\n        duration: 0.8\n    }, \"-=0.5\")\n    .to('#organize-headline', {\n        text: \"Ready.\",\n        duration: 0.8\n    });\n\n    // --- AI Executes Horizontal Scroll ---\n    const executeTrack = document.querySelector('#execute-horizontal');\n    gsap.to(executeTrack, {\n        xPercent: -100 * (document.querySelectorAll('.execute-panel').length - 1),\n        ease: 'none',\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#execute-container',\n            pin: true,\n            scrub: 1,\n            end: () => \"+=\" + executeTrack.offsetWidth\n        }\n    });\n\n    // --- Assistant Typing Effect ---\n    const chatWindow = document.querySelector('#chat-window');\n    const messages = [\n        { type: 'user', text: \"Plan my week. I have three major deadlines and a flight on Friday.\" },\n        { type: 'ai', text: \"Analyzing your workload... OK. I've rescheduled your non-critical syncs to next week and carved out 4-hour focus blocks each morning.\" },\n        { type: 'ai', text: \"I've also noticed you usually struggle with afternoon energy slumps, so I've placed the lighter tasks for the post-lunch window.\" }\n    ];\n\n    let currentMsg = 0;\n    const typeMessage = () => {\n        if (currentMsg >= messages.length) return;\n        \n        const msg = messages[currentMsg];\n        const bubble = document.createElement('div');\n        bubble.className = msg.type === 'user' ? 'flex justify-end' : 'flex justify-start';\n        bubble.innerHTML = `\n            <div class=\"${msg.type === 'user' ? 'bg-white/10' : 'bg-[#6C3AED]/20 border border-[#6C3AED]/30'} p-5 rounded-2xl ${msg.type === 'user' ? 'rounded-tr-none' : 'rounded-tl-none'} max-w-[80%]\">\n                <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed ${msg.type === 'ai' ? 'ai-text' : ''}\"></p>\n            </div>\n        `;\n        chatWindow.appendChild(bubble);\n        \n        const textTarget = bubble.querySelector('p');\n        gsap.to(textTarget, {\n            text: msg.text,\n            duration: msg.text.length * 0.02,\n            ease: 'none',\n            onComplete: () => {\n                currentMsg++;\n                setTimeout(typeMessage, 800);\n                chatWindow.scrollTo({ top: chatWindow.scrollHeight, behavior: 'smooth' });\n            }\n        });\n    };\n\n    ScrollTrigger.create({\n        trigger: '#assistant',\n        start: 'top center',\n        onEnter: () => typeMessage(),\n        once: true\n    });\n\n    // --- Transformation Graph Animation ---\n    gsap.to('.bar-after', {\n        height: (i, el) => el.dataset.height,\n        duration: 1.5,\n        stagger: 0.1,\n        ease: 'power4.out',\n        scrollTrigger: {\n            trigger: '#transformation',\n            start: 'top center'\n        }\n    });\n\n    // --- Marquee Setup ---\n    const marquee1 = document.querySelector('#marquee-1');\n    const marquee2 = document.querySelector('#marquee-2');\n    const testimonials = [\n        { name: \"Sarah Chen\", role: \"Product Lead @ Vercel\", quote: \"TaskMate literally added 2 hours back to my day.\" },\n        { name: \"David Miller\", role: \"DevOps @ Stripe\", quote: \"The AI prioritization is scary accurate.\" },\n        { name: \"Elena Rossi\", role: \"Designer @ Apple\", quote: \"Beautiful, fast, and actually useful.\" },\n        { name: \"Marcus Thorne\", role: \"Founder @ Stealth\", quote: \"I can't imagine working without it anymore.\" }\n    ];\n\n    const createTestimonial = (data) => {\n        return `\n            <div class=\"inline-block p-8 bg-[#F7F7F7] border border-[#E8E8E8] rounded-3xl w-[400px] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300\">\n                <p class=\"text-[#0A0A0A] font-bold mb-6 whitespace-normal\">\"${data.quote}\"</p>\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n                    <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=${data.name}\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full\" />\n                    <div>\n                        <p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#0A0A0A]\">${data.name}</p>\n                        <p class=\"text-[10px] text-[#999] uppercase tracking-widest\">${data.role}</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        `;\n    };\n\n    marquee1.innerHTML = testimonials.map(t => createTestimonial(t)).join('') + testimonials.map(t => createTestimonial(t)).join('');\n    marquee2.innerHTML = [...testimonials].reverse().map(t => createTestimonial(t)).join('') + [...testimonials].reverse().map(t => createTestimonial(t)).join('');\n\n    gsap.to('#marquee-1', {\n        xPercent: -50,\n        repeat: -1,\n        duration: 20,\n        ease: 'none'\n    });\n    gsap.to('#marquee-2', {\n        xPercent: 0,\n        x: -marquee2.scrollWidth / 2,\n        repeat: -1,\n        duration: 25,\n        ease: 'none',\n        startAt: { x: 0 }\n    });\n\n    // --- Dark Nav Toggle ---\n    ScrollTrigger.create({\n        trigger: 'section',\n        start: 'top 80',\n        onUpdate: (self) => {\n            const currentSection = self.trigger;\n            if(!currentSection) return;\n            const bg = window.getComputedStyle(currentSection).backgroundColor;\n            const isDark = bg === 'rgb(10, 10, 10)';\n            gsap.to('.dark-nav-text', { color: isDark ? '#ffffff' : '#0A0A0A', duration: 0.3 });\n        }\n    });\n\n    // Particle Drift Field for CTA\n    const ctaParticles = document.querySelector('#cta-particles');\n    for(let i=0; i<30; i++) {\n        const p = document.createElement('div');\n        p.className = 'absolute w-1 h-1 bg-white/40 rounded-full particle';\n        gsap.set(p, { left: random(0,100)+'%', top: random(0,100)+'%' });\n        ctaParticles.appendChild(p);\n    }\n    \n    document.querySelectorAll('.particle').forEach((p) => {\n        gsap.to(p, {\n            x: () => random(-50, 50),\n            y: () => random(-50, 50),\n            duration: () => random(5, 10),\n            repeat: -1,\n            yoyo: true,\n            ease: 'sine.inOut'\n        });\n    });\n\n</script>\n",
